<h2>Welcome to the V-Excel Library!</h2>

<p>The V-Excel library database holds a collection of about 1,900 books,
magazines, and journals. </p>

<h2>Borrowing Resources</h2>

<p>Library resources may be borrowed by our registered students or parents of children in KLC, Remedial Center or
in the LD Clinic for a three-week period. Please visit our library in Mandaveli and an office
volunteer will be happy to help you with the check-out process.</p>

<h2>Searching the Library</h2>

<p>You may view our resources by entering a specific title or author in
the <b>Search</b> box, or you may view all titles for a particular
category using the <b>Browse</b> box. To look at more information on the
resource, click on <b>View</b> link.

<h2>Other Resources</h2>

<p>If you are looking for a specific title which we don't have, please email us and we'll try and accomodate your
request.</p>

<h2>Donating to the Library</h2>

<p>Our organization accepts donations of books, magazines, videos, assessments, educational software 
and other resources from the general public. If you are interested in donating, please contact us.</p>
